{\displaystyle \nabla \times \mathbf {E} ={\hat {\mathbf {k} }}\times \mathbf {E} _{0}f'\left(\mathbf {k} \cdot \mathbf {r} -\omega t\right)=-{\frac {\partial \mathbf {B} }{\partial t}}\,\!}

